        "rich_text_HcBHYX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>When a string of diamonds came together, the queen of bracelets was formed! <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/tennis-bracelets\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Tennis Bracelets</span></a> are the most exquisite diamond Jewelry. They can be showstoppers on grand occasions as well as be the quiet, staple luxury Jewelry piece as you leap towards greater success. This ultimate guide to Tennis Bracelets cover everything you need to know about diamond bracelets - how to style your Tennis Bracelets, the different diamond cuts and how to choose the one that would suit you, different diamond setting based on your lifestyle and styling choices, and a step by step guide to buy a Tennis Diamond Bracelet.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_raQWyJ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "A Variety of Cuts in Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelets ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>A Variety of Cuts in Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelets </h2><p>Diamond Tennis Bracelets come in various diamond cuts! Choosing a Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelet means you are choosing enhanced beauty, more variety of cuts, and a more sustainable choice. </p>",
            "custom_id": "cuts"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_FcqBnM": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/A_Variety_of_Cuts_in_Lab_Grown_Diamond_Tennis_Bracelets_1080_600_33492e82-e88b-4647-b449-061f0272be4c.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Tennis Bracelets are commonly made in round cuts as they are radiant because of the optimal light reflection. <br/>Since a Tennis Bracelet shows a continuous flow of diamonds, the Round Cut Diamonds align beautifully in a line. If you want a classic and versatile piece of jewelry or want to gift it to someone, a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/products/elegant-round-diamond-tennis-bracelet\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Elegant Round Cut Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelet\">Round-Cut Tennis Bracelet</a> can be the perfect choice for you.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_e66geC": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>At Lucira, every diamond is cut with precision, with extra emphasis on customer experience, research and innovation, we bring an exclusive collection of Diamond Bracelets with various cuts and settings. For a more elongated and sleeker look than a Round Cut Diamond Bracelet, our Oval Cut Tennis Bracelets for Women is designed to flatter every wrist. To keep the diamonds secure, we have designed a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/products/oval-diamond-bezel-set-bracelet\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bezel Set Oval Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelets\">Bezel Set Oval Diamond Tennis Bracelet</a> with 30 brilliant diamonds, a special piece of jewelry designed for woman in sports and with an active lifestyle. <br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_XXQnUW": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/A_Variety_of_Cuts_in_Lab_Grown_Diamond_Tennis_Bracelets_2_1080_800_80175e2b-1a0a-44e0-b5ac-391126a505c4.jpg",
            "text": "<p>The emerald cut is elegance redefined as the step facets sit on the wrist gaining undivided attention. The Lucira Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelets come in many more settings and cuts such as the glimmering <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/products/glimmering-pear-shape-diamond-tennis-bracelet\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Pear Shaped Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelets\">Pear Shaped Diamond Bracelet </a>and <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/products/heart-cut-diamond-bezel-set-tennis-bracelet\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Heart Cut Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelet\">Heart Cut Diamond Tennis Bracelet</a>, the perfect gift for your significant other. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_fjrneh": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Choose A Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelet for Women",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Choose A Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelet for Women</h2>",
            "custom_id": "choose"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_RXTQWR": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Quality of Diamond",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Quality of Diamond</h3>",
            "custom_id": "quality"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_KtcB4U": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Quality of Diamond",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Untitled_1080_x_300_px.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Choosing the right Diamond Tennis Bracelet depends a lot on personal style, craftsmanship and how detailed the design is. Start by considering the diamond quality by checking the <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/blogs/stories/4cs-of-diamond\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"4C's of Lab Grown Diamond\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">4C’s of Diamonds</span></a> - Cut, Clarity, Carat and Color.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_zzBYcT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Choice of Metal",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Choice of Metal</h3>",
            "custom_id": "metal"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_WaD3LF": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Choice of Metal",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3_Metal_b071f7f8-3e24-4935-b0b9-befa6990cec3.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Next, decide which metal you want to choose and the metal setting. We, at Lucira jewelry, provide luxurious looks with jewelry only in Gold or Platinum. White Gold and Platinum give a modern twist to jewelry with the versatility to wear from grand occasions to work meetings, from western outfits to ethnic attires.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9ib4Q8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Choose Your Design and Fit",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Choose Your Design and Fit</h3>",
            "custom_id": "choose"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_WfcwfN": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Choose_Your_Design_and_Fit_1080_300.jpg",
            "text": "<h3></h3><p>Tennis bracelets come in different settings such as prongs and bezel set, and different cuts and designs such as a cascading design with a row of bracelets breathtakingly creating a ‘cascading’ effect while reflecting more shine. Each design is beautifully crafted, so choose a Tennis Bracelet that appeals to your style. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "design",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_yKa97p": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Having the right fit is important. A tight bracelet may feel uncomfortable and a loose fit may slip off. A snug fit will provide comfort and look dainty. We curated a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/pages/how-to-wear-2\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">How to Wear Guide</span></a> for you to choose the perfect fit for your bracelets. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_AQhaK9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Check the Certification",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Check the Certification</h3>",
            "custom_id": "certification"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_iP7Rb3": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/LGD_Certificate.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Ensure that any jewelry that you buy is certified by SGI, IGI, GIA or any reputed and trusted institutions. These certifications ensure that you are getting real diamonds. Your certified jewelry undergoes evaluation under strict set standards, ensuring the best quality.<br/></p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_k9TjGr": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Care and Maintenance of Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelet",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Care and Maintenance of Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelet</h2><p>At Lucira Jewelry, we craft pieces that are meant to last a lifetime and even be passed down generations.</p>",
            "custom_id": "care"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_tQdgCU": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/a093dd59-a41f-44cf-95d0-c41e9ff593c4.jpg",
            "text": "<p> A little care goes a long way in helping us keep the promise of brilliance. Use a lint-free cloth, preferably the high quality wiping cloth that came with your Lucira piece to wipe your Tennis Bracelet. While all our jewelry is designed to move with you and not be contained to lockers, when the jewelry is not in use, store them in a soft lined pouch or a jewelry box. Our Lucira Jewelry box reflects the luxury we promise, along with being a safe home for the bracelets to sit in when not in use.</p><p>Use the ‘last on, first off’ rule to extend the life of your jewelry. It means you should put on your tennis bracelet after putting on makeup, dressing up and applying perfume, and take it off first while undressing. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7j96wz": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>To keep your jewelry secure, avoid wearing jewelry pieces during workouts or swimming. This maintenance is unnecessary for our <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/sports-collection\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">On The Move</span></a> collection. Our On The Move collection features jewelry pieces, no matter the number of diamonds in the Tennis Bracelets, that stay secure during your active lifestyle. This has been researched and tested for over 2500 hours, so that you never have to take off your treasured jewelry pieces. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7JTBag": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>Whether you are celebrating a milestone or want to gift yourself or someone something luxurious, a diamond tennis bracelet is a symbol of elegance and personal experience. With Lucira’s commitment to innovation, quality craftmanship and sustainability, our lab grown diamond tennis bracelets are an experience of feeling pure joy every time you look at it,no matter how long it’s been.  </p><p>Explore the Lucira collection - where love, comfort and joy are crafted in every diamond piece. </p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion"
          }
        }
      },
